x/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/24/02 10:38:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3796.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://home.earthlink.net/~eddytaylor/data/deadbernie.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Mythic and changes in game thoughts and a question</span><hr size=1> I think the detect hidden radius on an archer with average stealth at lvl 50 is something like 2700... clip distance is like 3000, correct? And what are you complaining about again? <p><TABLE><TR><TD><FONT COLOR="#151515">----------------------------------------------------------------------</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD><FONT COLOR="#151515">Wulien, lvl 48 Rogue of <A HREF="http://www.norrathfellowship.com">Norrath Fellowship</A> on Quellious</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD><FONT COLOR="#151515">W.U.L.I.E.N.: Wireless Unit Limited to Infiltration and Efficient Nullification</FONT></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BGCOLOR="#000000"><TR><TD><CENTER><FONT COLOR="#303030">.<FONT COLOR="#393939">.<FONT COLOR="#606060">.<FONT COLOR="#707070">B<FONT COLOR="#808080">e<FONT COLOR="#909090">r<FONT COLOR="#999999">n<FONT COLOR="#A9A9A9">a<FONT COLOR="#D2D2D2">r<FONT COLOR="#D4D4D4">d <FONT COLOR="#006000">R<FONT COLOR="#007000">a<FONT COLOR="#008000">z<FONT COLOR="#009000">o<FONT COLOR="#009000">r<FONT COLOR="#00FC00">l<FONT COLOR="#00B200">e<FONT COLOR="#00C800">a<FONT COLOR="#00D400">f<FONT COLOR="#00E800">.<FONT COLOR="#00F300">.<FONT COLOR="#00FF00">.</TD></CENTER></TR><TR><TD><FONT COLOR=#808080><CENTER>Ranger of <a href="http://pub18.ezboard.com/bfalleneagles">Fallen Eagles</a></CENTER></TD></TR></TD></TR><TR><TD><FONT COLOR=#F0F0F0><CENTER>Gawaine</CENTER></TD></TR></TABLE></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uubergnome563.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ubergnome563</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/24/02 10:56:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3796.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> .</span><hr size=1> how about the volatile nature of the game for starters?<br><br>One day you your class does this thing... the next morning you are something totally different.  Too bad you couldnt spec accordingly until this respec goes live.  <br><br>Patches like the 2.x spec point patch, 1.50-1.51, and several others involving relic keeps and such have completely changed certain aspects of the game, and now they make retro changes and retro retro changes and it never settles down to stable.  Do you want to invest time in character that in 1.5 months will be nothing like you intended him/her to be?  Critblades are a good example of this, but I would hate to be that pure tank that spec'd shield up to 50 because of its pve performance waaaaay back in the day...<br><br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umelanu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>melanu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/25/02 10:05:03 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3796.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> Wulien,<br><br>I commented on that one change, but it's the nature of the way they make this game that bothers me.  Truesight and see hidden never should have gone in as they were either one.<br><br>This change is another example of them completely changing somehting..it does not tone it down..or modify it in a small way to try and improve the situation..it completely reverses the situation.<br><br>Second, I am level 50 and I don't see mid 40s archers in my team from that far off, much less enemies.  It may be that this is what you were told/saw but it's far from my experience.  <br><br>I have an archer and I am all for archers being powerful, but changes like this hurt the game.  Just as see hidden going in hurt the game.  I argued against it and I don't have it in part because I don't like it.  <br><br>I do think a fix was in order but to just negate it completely minus 10minutes after combat?  It would have been much better to adjust the range.  I would be happy with 75% of bow shot range for see hidden and bow shot range for TS myself this seems fair.  I also think fine give archers camo but they can't move or use TS while it's on.  Moving breaks camo. TS breaks stealth.<br><br>Mel<br><br> <p>The only sure bulwark of continuing liberty is a government strong enough to protect the interests of the people, and a people strong enough and well enough informed to maintain its sovereign control over the government. Franklin Delano Roosevelt</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ucaxus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caxus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/25/02 2:52:34 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm19.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3796.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: .</span><hr size=1> Melanu, i couldn't agree more.  Mythic has no concept of making small adjustments and waiting to see the impact.  The nerf to the cleric AE mez is a perfect example.  Out of the blue they changed the recast time from 30 seconds to 300 seconds.  Now my jaw hit the floor when i saw this because how 